Summari.es - Readme file

Project homepage: http://summari.es

Get instant summaries of articles, blog posts, or websites right in your browser.

Summari.es is a bookmarklet that takes the text of whatever web page you're looking at and summarizes the text into three sentences.

Summari.es uses the TopicMarks API to do the initial summary heavy lifting.



